Data type   size    Range
int         2 or 4  -32768 to 32767
float       5       -3.4x10*38 to 3.4x10*38
double      8       -1.7x10*-308 to 1.7x10*308 **indices
char        1       -128 to 127
bool        undefined   true or false 1 and 0

the sizes are in byte ex int is 4 bytes 4 x 8 = 32-bits 
Bit - 1 or 0 true or false
Nible - 4 bits
Byte - 8 bits
Kilobyte - 1,024 bytes